          keyTakeaway: "Covered Calls generate monthly income from existing holdings. Protective Puts insure your portfolio against crash risk.",
          example: "Owning ₹50 lakh of Nifty stocks with no hedge. Market crashes 20% = ₹10 lakh loss. Buying 2-month Puts for ₹80,000 as insurance: Puts gain ₹9 lakh in crash = net loss only ₹80,000. Insurance works."
